Inside the while loop, after printing "Too high" or "Too low", prompt the user again and call input.nextInt() to update guess. For example:

while (guess != answer) {
    if (guess < answer) {
        System.out.println("Too low, try again.");
    } else {
        System.out.println("Too high, try again.");
    }
    System.out.print("Guess my number: ");
    guess = input.nextInt();  // read a new guess
}

